    <category>
        <pattern>* REGISTRATION ^</pattern>
        <template>
            <think><set name="topic">registration</set></think>
            <srai><star/> IT <star index="2"/></srai>
        </template>
    </category>
    
	<topic name="registration">
	   <category>
            <pattern>* SOMETHING ^ ABOUT IT ^</pattern>
            <template><srai>WHAT IS IT</srai></template>
        </category>
        
	    <category>
	        <pattern>^ WHAT IS IT ^</pattern>
	        <template>By registering a course, you express your interest in this course. <srai>WHAT IS IT GOOD FOR</srai></template>
        </category>
        
        <category>
            <pattern>^ WHAT IS IT GOOD FOR ^</pattern>
            <template>When the number of students who want to enroll a course with limited capacity exceeds its capacity, the students who registered the course first will be favored.</template>
        </category>
        
        <category>
            <pattern>* BENEFITS OF IT ^</pattern>
            <template><srai>WHAT IS IT GOOD FOR</srai></template>
        </category>
        
        <category>
            <pattern>* NEED IT ^</pattern>
            <template><srai>WHAT IS IT GOOD FOR</srai></template>
        </category>
        
        <category>
            <pattern>* USE OF IT ^</pattern>
            <template><srai>WHAT IS IT GOOD FOR</srai></template>
        </category>
        
        <category>
            <pattern>* IT NEEDED ^</pattern>
            <template><srai>WHAT IS IT GOOD FOR</srai></template>
        </category>
        
        <category>
            <pattern>* IT OPTIONAL ^</pattern>
            <template>The registration of courses is optional. However, it is highly recommended for courses with limited capacity.</template>
        </category>

        <category>
            <pattern>* IT REQUIRED ^</pattern>
            <template><srai>IS IT OPTIONAL</srai></template>
        </category>

        <category>
            <pattern>* IT COMPULSORY ^</pattern>
            <template><srai>IS IT OPTIONAL</srai></template>
        </category>
        
        <category>
            <pattern>* IT VOLUNTARY ^</pattern>
            <template><srai>IS IT OPTIONAL</srai></template>
        </category>
        
        <category>
        <pattern>^ WHEN ^ IT ^</pattern>
        <template>
            Courses are registered during the period "Registration for courses". This period can be found in the schedule. 
            Please, mind that in the first semesters, your Registration period begins a few days later than specified in schedule because of the <set name="topic">registration waves</set>.
            <button>
                <text>Click here to show schedule</text>
                <url>https://is.muni.cz/auth/predmety/obdobi</url>
            </button>
        </template>
        </category>

    	<category>
    	    <pattern>*</pattern>
    	    <template>Unfortunately, I cannot help you with this question. You can try asking differently or try to find the answer here: 
    	        <link>
    	            <text>HELP - Registration and Enrollment</text> 
    	            <url>https://is.muni.cz/auth/help/student/registrace?lang=en</url>
                </link>
    	    </template>
        </category>
	</topic>
	
</aiml>